## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on available online resources, which may not capture the full scope of human trafficking due to its hidden nature. Additionally, the data on human trafficking is often estimated, leading to potential discrepancies in reported figures. Further research and collaboration among international organizations, governments, and NGOs are necessary to obtain more accurate data and develop effective strategies to combat human trafficking.

